reviewText: Really enjoyed this one. The host offers a different perspective than what you would normally expect out of a travel video, so keep this in mind.

This DVD is worth, maybe, 99 cents. Cheap production, half as long as it should be. Buy a good travel book and leave this DVD for the scrap heap.
I wish I had saved my money.
Very good & fairly indepth look at both cities not a touristy DVD as much as it is informative.
